  "title": "A round orange UFO observed by two people in Iguarapava-SP [2001]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/13/a-round-orange-ufo-observed-by-two-people-in-iguarapava-sp-2001/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-pQ",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 7th, 2001</strong>. Time: 6:30 pm. Duration: 5 to 10 minutes. Under good visibility conditions, an unidentified flying object was sighted over the city of Iguarapava, State of São Paulo, by two witnesses. They reported a round orange UFO that was &#8220;bigger than an airplane&#8221; and it was approximately 20km from the observation point, going from North to Southwest.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.592. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni na cidade de Iguarapava, São Paulo”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>JAN 7th, 2001. Time: 6:30 pm. Duration: 5 to 10 minutes. Under good visibility conditions, an unidentified flying object was sighted over the city of Iguarapava, State of São Paulo, by two witnesses. They reported a round orange UFO that was &#8220;bigger than an airplane&#8221; and it was approximately 20km from the observation point, going [&hellip;]</p>\n",
